{"tid":849910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惹怒非洲鄉民3中國人被打死　恐怖影像曝光 由黃皮膚打到黑皮膚 求片","createTime":"2018-10-06T05:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T16:02:39.000Z","uid":72009,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8714ea9ea6ce0af70c680916510b813477b20b","tid":849910,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"《美聯社》與《美國之音》報導，事發在本周四，一群由約10名中國男子組成的團隊，聘請當地的青年領袖、國民議會第二副議長的弟弟伊格納斯‧迪姆貝勒-納科(Dimbele-Nakoe)做嚮導，帶著他們從村莊沿著卡代河，前往一處金礦探勘。不料在航行途中小船翻覆，迪姆貝勒-納科失蹤，但之後發現他的遺體。這群中國人員之後回到當地警局作筆錄，但當地鄉民都相信，是這群中國人害死了迪姆貝勒-納科，因此發動攻擊。最後導致3名中國男子死亡，另外有3名中國人受傷，當地曝光的照片更可見，有中國人被打到從黃皮膚變成黑皮膚。<br />\n迪姆貝勒-納科的哥哥馬蘇林(Mathurin Dimbele-Nakoe)表示，這群中國人是蘇索-納坎博(Sosso-Nakombo)地區的礦業公司人員。政府發言人卡札吉(Ange Maxime Kazagui)就強調，施暴者一定會受到懲罰，另外目前中國駐中非首都班基的大使館，目前尚未對此事做出回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181006/1442760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181006%2F1442760&d=gp6lRm7seQHhmILTjdPMLBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=954531c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181006%2F1442760&h=a408826e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181006/1442760</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9c17547a524198d093fda426c0bb832c4f292a","tid":849910,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46918e903a66e330b8b34998b63dcfc9076fc99f","tid":849910,"uid":49994,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"被打到從黃皮膚變成黑皮膚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6d4091627bd17bbcbefbde3d111e76f8530c18","tid":849910,"uid":52358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sc